Bits and pieces for testing xzibit.  None of these will probably make it into the final product.

Xzibit_2007.jpg: photo of Xzibit, (c) Sjoerd ten Kate from London, licensed under cc-by-sa.
noddy-rfb-server.py: an RFB server that sends you a photo of Xzibit
state-toggle.c: an app which can switch the _XZIBIT_SHARE setting of its window
xzibit-bus-server.py: a simple Unix domain bus server, used before we get stuck into tubes
xzibit-bus-client.py: test for xzibit-bus-server.py; not the real-life client

